### Messages (Threads, Read Status, RLS/thread_participants)

**Source of Truth:**
- `app/messages/page.tsx` (330 lГӯneas, Server Component)
- `app/messages/ThreadPanel.tsx` (Server Component)
- `app/messages/[thread_id]/page.tsx` (173 lГӯneas, Server Component)
