| `/profiles/[user_id]` | PГәblica | Detalle de perfil + lista de listings del usuario | Ninguno |
| `/listings` | PГәblica | Lista de listings con bГәsqueda y filtros (q, city, zone, type, min, max, sort) | Ninguno |
| `/listings/new` | Protegida | Formulario crear listing (title, description, city, zone, price, type) | `requireProfileOrRedirect()` |
| `/listings/[id]` | PГәblica | Detalle de listing + perfil del autor + botГіn Contactar | Ninguno |
| `/messages` | Protegida | Inbox con lista de threads (conversaciones) | `requireProfileOrRedirect()` |
| `/messages/[thread_id]` | Protegida | Chat thread individual (historial + form enviar mensaje) | `requireProfileOrRedirect()` + validaciГіn participant |
| `/debug/supabase` | PГәblica (dev only) | PГЎgina de debug para probar conexiГіn Supabase (bloqueada en producciГіn) | `NODE_ENV === 'production'` вҶ’ `notFound()` |

**Rutas legales/placeholder:**
- `/legal/terms` - TГ©rminos y condiciones (placeholder)
- `/legal/privacy` - PolГӯtica de privacidad (placeholder)
- `/security` - InformaciГіn de seguridad (placeholder)

---

## 5. Modelo de datos (resumen)

### Tabla `profiles`

**DescripciГіn:** Perfil pГәblico del usuario

**Campos principales:**
- `user_id` (UUID, PK, FK вҶ’ `auth.users`)
- `display_name` (TEXT, NOT NULL)
- `city` (TEXT, NOT NULL)
- `zone` (TEXT, NOT NULL)
- `avatar_url` (TEXT, nullable)
- `pets` (BOOLEAN, nullable)
- `smoker` (BOOLEAN, nullable)
- `cleanliness` (SMALLINT, 1-3, nullable)
- `parties` (BOOLEAN, nullable)
- `schedule` (TEXT, 'day'\|'night', nullable)
- `created_at` (TIMESTAMPTZ, default NOW())
- `updated_at` (TIMESTAMPTZ, default NOW(), trigger automГЎtico)

**RLS:**
- **SELECT**: PГәblico (todos pueden leer para explorar)
- **INSERT/UPDATE/DELETE**: Solo dueГұo (`auth.uid() = user_id`)

**ГҚndices:**
- `profiles_city_idx`
- `profiles_zone_idx`
- `profiles_city_zone_idx`

### Tabla `listings`

**DescripciГіn:** Anuncios de cuartos disponibles o bГәsqueda de roomie

**Campos principales:**
- `id` (UUID, PK)
- `user_id` (UUID, FK вҶ’ `auth.users`)
- `title` (TEXT, NOT NULL)
- `description` (TEXT, NOT NULL)
- `city` (TEXT, NOT NULL)
- `zone` (TEXT, NOT NULL)
- `price_mxn` (INTEGER, nullable)
- `listing_type` (TEXT, 'room'\|'roommate')
- `created_at` (TIMESTAMPTZ, default NOW())
- `updated_at` (TIMESTAMPTZ, default NOW())

**RLS:**
- **SELECT**: PГәblico (todos pueden leer listings)
- **INSERT/UPDATE/DELETE**: Solo dueГұo (`auth.uid() = user_id`)

### Tabla `threads`

**DescripciГіn:** ConversaciГіn entre dos usuarios (opcionalmente vinculada a un listing)

**Campos principales:**
- `id` (UUID, PK)
- `user1_id` (UUID, FK вҶ’ `auth.users`)
- `user2_id` (UUID, FK вҶ’ `auth.users`)
- `listing_id` (UUID, FK вҶ’ `listings`, nullable)
- `created_at` (TIMESTAMPTZ, default NOW())

**RLS:**
- **SELECT**: Solo participantes (`auth.uid() = user1_id OR auth.uid() = user2_id`)
- **INSERT**: Solo participantes
- **UPDATE/DELETE**: Denegado (MVP)

**ГҚndices:**
- `threads_users_idx` (user1_id, user2_id)
- `threads_unique_idx` UNIQUE (LEAST(user1_id, user2_id), GREATEST(user1_id, user2_id), COALESCE(listing_id, default UUID))

### Tabla `messages`

**DescripciГіn:** Mensajes dentro de un thread

**Campos principales:**
- `id` (UUID, PK)
- `thread_id` (UUID, FK вҶ’ `threads`, CASCADE)
- `sender_id` (UUID, FK вҶ’ `auth.users`)
- `body` (TEXT, NOT NULL)
- `created_at` (TIMESTAMPTZ, default NOW())

**RLS:**
- **SELECT**: Solo si `auth.uid()` es participante del thread
- **INSERT**: `sender_id` debe ser `auth.uid()` Y participante del thread
- **UPDATE/DELETE**: Denegado (MVP)

**ГҚndices:**
- `messages_thread_created_idx` (thread_id, created_at)

### Relaciones entre tablas

```
auth.users (1) в”Җв”Җ> (1) profiles.user_id
auth.users (1) в”Җв”Җ> (*) listings.user_id
auth.users (1) в”Җв”Җ> (*) threads.user1_id
auth.users (1) в”Җв”Җ> (*) threads.user2_id
auth.users (1) в”Җв”Җ> (*) messages.sender_id

listings (1) в”Җв”Җ> (*) threads.listing_id (nullable)
threads (1) в”Җв”Җ> (*) messages.thread_id (CASCADE)
```

---

## 6. Flujo de usuario (end-to-end)

### Usuario nuevo desde signup

1. **Landing (`/`)** вҶ’ Click "Crear perfil" вҶ’ `/signup`
2. **Signup (`/signup`)**:
   - Llenar email, password, confirm password, checkbox tГ©rminos
   - Click "Registrarse"
   - Mensaje: "Revisa tu correo para verificar"
3. **Email verification**: Click en link de Supabase
4. **Login (`/login`)**:
   - Email/password
   - Verifica `email_confirmed_at`
   - Si OK вҶ’ `router.refresh()` вҶ’ `hasProfile()` вҶ’ redirect a `/onboarding/step-1`

### Onboarding step-1 вҶ’ step-2

1. **Step-1 (`/onboarding/step-1`)**:
   - Form: display_name, city, zone, avatar (file upload)
   - Guardar вҶ’ `saveMyProfile()` вҶ’ redirect a `/onboarding/step-2`
2. **Step-2 (`/onboarding/step-2`)**:
   - Form: pets (SГӯ/No), smoker (SГӯ/No), cleanliness (1-3), parties (SГӯ/No), schedule (DГӯa/Noche)
   - Guardar вҶ’ `saveMyLifestyle()` вҶ’ redirect a `/explore`

### Explore / Listings

1. **Explore (`/explore`)**:
   - Lista de perfiles con avatar, nombre, ciudad, zona, badges de lifestyle
   - Filtros: bГәsqueda por nombre (q), city, zone
   - Click en perfil вҶ’ `/profiles/[user_id]`
2. **Listings (`/listings`)**:
   - Lista de listings con badge tipo, tГӯtulo, descripciГіn, precio, ciudad, zona
   - Filtros: q, city, zone, listing_type, min, max, sort (recent/price_asc/price_desc)
   - Click en listing вҶ’ `/listings/[id]`

### Contactar вҶ’ chat

1. **Desde listing (`/listings/[id]`)**:
   - Click "Contactar" вҶ’ `findOrCreateThread(listingUserId, listingId)`
   - Crea/busca thread вҶ’ redirect a `/messages/[thread_id]`
2. **Desde perfil (`/profiles/[user_id]`)**:
   - Click "Contactar" вҶ’ `findOrCreateThread(userId, null)`
   - Crea/busca thread вҶ’ redirect a `/messages/[thread_id]`
3. **Chat (`/messages/[thread_id]`)**:
   - Historial de mensajes (burbujas: azul propio, gris otro)
   - Form textarea + botГіn "Enviar"
   - `sendMessage(threadId, body)` вҶ’ `revalidatePath()`

### Logout

1. Click "Logout" en header вҶ’ `logout()` (server action) вҶ’ `router.replace('/login')` + `router.refresh()`
2. Header actualiza: desaparece user chip, Messages, muestra Login/Signup

---

